{"tid":2430776,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"原來馬體會蘇亞雷斯都支持香港人抗爭","createTime":"2021-03-03T07:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T09:37:38.000Z","uid":78243,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"de258a3a5be70a5e02e5eb05798d66e27f853f94","tid":2430776,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:23:16.000Z","msg":"阿蘇向皇馬下戰書：報仇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=32564723668\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D32564723668&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiugEOIADdcgve6BSnlMLQ7pQ%3D&h=a3cf88b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=32564723668</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now Sports】打吡大戰在即，馬德里體育會前鋒蘇亞雷斯表示很多球員對皇家馬德里都特別醒神，並揚言要復仇。<br />\n西甲榜首隊馬德里體育會於下周日聯賽主場對皇家馬德里，勝負左右爭標大局，前鋒蘇亞雷斯（Luis Suarez）透露所有隊友都躍躍欲試，想在主場一報作客負0:2之仇。阿蘇說：「對皇家馬德里的比賽總是特別的，大家都想在他們面前展示身價，所以十分期待。<br />\n<br />\n「我們要一報之前落敗之辱，告訴全世界我們想繼續佔據榜首。」這位烏拉圭球星以16個入球位居西甲射手榜次席，僅次於19球的巴塞隆拿巨星美斯。<br />\n<br />\n「我總想證明自己，不斷改善自己，不斷越過對手設下的障礙。很多人都不信馬德里體育會可以入這禱多入球，但身邊有如此出色的球員，其實入波並不難。」他續說。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22d533827dde91e0bb16226be4f0b8a9119c63a","tid":2430776,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b0a78ebf7aab1f292bbcd09fe76569d12b9211","tid":2430776,"uid":166262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:14:55.000Z","msg":"邊到講香港人事<br />\n報仇？"},{"pid":"4e83d82d1a15781e217928376737c40ab610ad54","tid":2430776,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:37:38.000Z","msg":"蘇狗手足黎<br />\